ior. For large flakes a\nmaximum value of interfacial shear stress (ISS) of 0.4 MPa is obtained prior to\nflake slipping.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2016 17:25:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-17"}
