ortance of diffusive processes in the burn-out of\nthe non-reacted pockets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2016 19:36:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Mar 2018 15:39:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-14"}
